div.div:
Game.js
- Import the assets
- map levels
- music
- templates
- Instanciate dynamically 2D array
- each case in the array contains instanciated
element created through DynamicElement.js,
via the levelmap structure.
- Provides methods to user
- Interprets the request from the server
and translate them to javascript method

assets
Folder conataining the assets (img and music) for a map level.
Structure of the folder :
- template1
-element1Img.png
-element2Img.png
-element3Img.png
- template2
- templateN
-music
- song1.mp3
- song2.mp3

maps
Each level contains a structure
of the map (element used, map pattern, name/song/template of the map)
Structure of the folder :
- level1.js
- level2.js
- pokemonTutorial.js
- levelX.js

div.div:
DynamicElement
Factory Class. Instanciate object from the elements available in the current map level. Game.js call the factory in the 2D array generation. Each case will contains a new element.

div.div:
elements
Contains the class of each element to interact with in the game.
Element are generated in the DynamicElement or manually in the game.
